Package: Khan
Title: Feature Selection on Graphs with FDR Control
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sinian", "Zhang", email = "zhan9381@umn.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Methods for false-discovery-rate controlled inference on
    subgraph features and persistent homology generators in Gaussian
    graphical models and Ising models.  Implements the BHq, DGS, and
    KHAN algorithms from Liang, Zhang, and Neykov (2024), along with
    debiased graphical-lasso estimation, Gaussian multiplier bootstrap
    baselines, and subgraph enumeration utilities.
